Gefen wannan SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, an kuma lura da abubuwan sake maye a cikin wasu HCoVs, wanda HCoVs suka sake haɗuwa da wasu CoVs na dabba a cikin abubuwan halittar da basu da tsari.
